snippet.textDisplay:
Merry Christmas/Happy Holidays you guys!

This video was very cathartic to watch, I love seeing people get rid of stuff that they just don't need (we are a species of hoarders, we're basically dragons lol)

I did my own spring clean on my backpacks this week, too. I (somehow) whittled down a 65L and 25L plus shoulder bag down to JUST a 30L and it feels good but my inner packrat wants to cry hahah.
